channel.title: Death To The Stock Photo
channel.description:
A blogger/designer friend and myself were sick of searching through cheesy stock photos of men in suits holding hands so we decided to launch a project to combat this modern atrocity. Free lifestyle photography to do whatever you please, all sent in monthly photo packs.
[Death To The Stock Photo][1]
[1]: http://www.join.deathtothestockphoto.com
